message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "llm-political-alignment-ca-es: Measuring the cross-lingual political shift of LLM APIs in Catalan and Spanish"
abstract: >-
  A framework to measure the cross-lingual political shift of LLM APIs in Catalan
  and Spanish — how much a model's distribution of answers to real political
  survey questions changes between the two languages — grounded in real survey
  data from CEO (Centre d'Estudis d'Opinió, Catalonia) and CIS (Centro de
  Investigaciones Sociológicas, Spain). It compares the model's answer
  distribution against the actual human population distribution across languages
  and perspective framings, following the survey-grounded cultural-alignment
  approach (MENAValues).
